"stderr`, use seu mĂŠtodo :meth:`~file.write`."

#: ../../library/os.rst:1900
msgid ""
"Write the contents of *buffers* to file descriptor *fd*. *buffers* must be a "
"sequence of :term:`bytes-like objects <bytes-like object>`. Buffers are "
