"sistemas de arquivos de rede, que retornam ``dirent.d_type == DT_UNKNOWN``."

#: ../../library/os.rst:3031
msgid ""
"Return ``True`` if this entry is a junction (even if broken); return "
"``False`` if the entry points to a regular directory, any kind of file, a "
