"O mĂłdulo padrĂŁo :mod:`stat` define funĂ§Ăľes e constantes que sĂŁo Ăşteis para "
"extrair informaĂ§Ăľes de uma estrutura :c:struct:`stat`. (No Windows, alguns "
"itens sĂŁo preenchidos com valores fictĂ­cios.)"

#: ../../library/os.rst:3332
msgid ""
"For backward compatibility, a :class:`stat_result` instance is also "
"accessible as a tuple of at least 10 integers giving the most important (and "
"portable) members of the :c:struct:`stat` structure, in the order :attr:"
