#: ../../library/os.rst:5412
msgid "This function should be employed only if :func:`WIFEXITED` is true."
msgstr ""
"Esta funĂ§ĂŁo deve ser empregada apenas se :func:`WIFEXITED` for verdadeira."

#: ../../library/os.rst:5419
msgid "Return the signal which caused the process to stop."
msgstr "Retorna o sinal que causou a interrupĂ§ĂŁo do processo."

#: ../../library/os.rst:5421
msgid "This function should be employed only if :func:`WIFSTOPPED` is true."
msgstr ""
"Esta funĂ§ĂŁo deve ser empregada apenas se :func:`WIFSTOPPED` for verdadeira."

#: ../../library/os.rst:5428
msgid "Return the number of the signal that caused the process to terminate."
msgstr "Retorna o nĂşmero do sinal que causou o encerramento do processo."

#: ../../library/os.rst:5436
